{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-detail-tsx","path":"/detail/2a5503bf-4c05-5301-82f8-ca1670eb4060","result":{"pageContext":{"html":"<h1>前言</h1>\n<p><code>Node.js</code>是作为一个前端开发者必备的技术栈。</p>\n<p>正如官方中说的那样，<code>Node.js</code>是一个基于 Chrome V8 引擎的 JavaScript 运行时。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Node.js® is a JavaScript runtime built on <a href=\"https://v8.dev/\">Chrome's V8 JavaScript engine</a>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><code>Node.js</code>让 JavaScript 代码可以脱离浏览器，在其他环境运行，这也是前端工程化的基础</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/d4a4a9be5e9f5db070fe1e9a9ceaffb7/5a190/2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 43.24324324324324%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/d4a4a9be5e9f5db070fe1e9a9ceaffb7/fcda8/2.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/d4a4a9be5e9f5db070fe1e9a9ceaffb7/12f09/2.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/d4a4a9be5e9f5db070fe1e9a9ceaffb7/e4a3f/2.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/d4a4a9be5e9f5db070fe1e9a9ceaffb7/fcda8/2.png 590w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/d4a4a9be5e9f5db070fe1e9a9ceaffb7/5a190/2.png 800w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h1>环境安装</h1>\n<p>进入<code>node.js</code>官方 <a href=\"https://nodejs.org/en/\">https://nodejs.org/en/</a> ，他会自动根据你的环境推荐安装包。<code>windows</code>环境推荐选择<code>.msi</code>后缀的安装文件，安装过程就是一路确定到底就可以了。<code>mac</code>推荐使用<code>HomeBrew</code>下载<del>HomeBrew 真香</del></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/a4fc0c42e8f0e5de443803473e42ba53/d0143/1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.21621621621621%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/a4fc0c42e8f0e5de443803473e42ba53/fcda8/1.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/a4fc0c42e8f0e5de443803473e42ba53/12f09/1.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/a4fc0c42e8f0e5de443803473e42ba53/e4a3f/1.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/a4fc0c42e8f0e5de443803473e42ba53/fcda8/1.png 590w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/a4fc0c42e8f0e5de443803473e42ba53/efc66/1.png 885w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/a4fc0c42e8f0e5de443803473e42ba53/d0143/1.png 1025w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>安装成功后，打开一个终端，windows 上可以选择<code>cmd</code>或<code>powershell</code> ,输入</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-bash line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-bash\">node -v</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>如果有 node 版本结果，则安装成功。</p>\n<p>具体步骤：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>按住 win+R</li>\n<li>输入 <code>cmd</code> 或者 <code>powershell</code></li>\n<li>输入<code>node -v</code></li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 454px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/6c2ebcca2723c6ea53ff02bc7f350ee0/b3c1d/3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 69.5945945945946%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/6c2ebcca2723c6ea53ff02bc7f350ee0/b3c1d/3.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/6c2ebcca2723c6ea53ff02bc7f350ee0/12f09/3.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/6c2ebcca2723c6ea53ff02bc7f350ee0/e4a3f/3.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/6c2ebcca2723c6ea53ff02bc7f350ee0/b3c1d/3.png 454w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 454px) 100vw, 454px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h1>初次使用</h1>\n<p>试试直接在终端中直接输入<code>node</code>，就会进入这个界面。这是 node.js 交互式解释器，可能用过<code>python</code>的同学就会有点熟悉了。我们可以直接输入<code>JavaScript</code>代码并执行，而不需要浏览器环境。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 534px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/3fd1240d2dfdc23380ccefb5ee239fb7/a07a7/4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 32.43243243243243%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAGCAIAAABM9SnKAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAkElEQVQY072PwQrCMAyG09XaQw8i0rWCdFspuBUG7XrobtP3fyl/POrAm9/pD8lHEjqH0yXer4+n3Tbv/ZKzlLJpmuMbZCEE5/ywB6Wc4KScb86FEGqtzjlr7TAMxphpmrTWRMQYo28glFKUUpiDAK3runEckdu2jTHO84wSC3DOp9z3/bquCDu9n8DBV/R/Xi93D16FkpDAAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/3fd1240d2dfdc23380ccefb5ee239fb7/a07a7/4.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/3fd1240d2dfdc23380ccefb5ee239fb7/12f09/4.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/3fd1240d2dfdc23380ccefb5ee239fb7/e4a3f/4.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/3fd1240d2dfdc23380ccefb5ee239fb7/a07a7/4.png 534w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 534px) 100vw, 534px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 576px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/2b9edb903f16da72fdeb6d97b142e39d/533c1/5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.72972972972974%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/2b9edb903f16da72fdeb6d97b142e39d/533c1/5.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/2b9edb903f16da72fdeb6d97b142e39d/12f09/5.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/2b9edb903f16da72fdeb6d97b142e39d/e4a3f/5.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/2b9edb903f16da72fdeb6d97b142e39d/533c1/5.png 576w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>和<code>python</code>类似，我们不仅可以这样一行一行执行，也可以用来执行一个 JavaScript 文件，我们可以通过在终端中执行<code>node &#x3C;文件名></code>来执行文件，或者使用 vs code 中的 插件<code>Code Runner</code>来运行。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 340px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/0c4f074d849967efe5ac480e13015dec/9f933/6.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.02702702702703%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/0c4f074d849967efe5ac480e13015dec/9f933/6.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/0c4f074d849967efe5ac480e13015dec/12f09/6.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/0c4f074d849967efe5ac480e13015dec/e4a3f/6.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/0c4f074d849967efe5ac480e13015dec/9f933/6.png 340w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 340px) 100vw, 340px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h1>node 环境和浏览器环境的区别</h1>\n<p>node 环境中的少了浏览器中的一些 api，像<code>document</code>,<code>window</code>,<code>alert</code>,<code>history</code>都是不支持的。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 506px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/c86c39254cee817a25d0120f99ee135f/29f4e/7.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 49.32432432432432%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/c86c39254cee817a25d0120f99ee135f/29f4e/7.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/c86c39254cee817a25d0120f99ee135f/12f09/7.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/c86c39254cee817a25d0120f99ee135f/e4a3f/7.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/c86c39254cee817a25d0120f99ee135f/29f4e/7.png 506w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 506px) 100vw, 506px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>但是它也增加了许多特性。像 I/O 读写和模块加载之类的东西。</p>\n<p>这是使用 node.js 读取文本文件。<del>这就比用 C 语言简单多了</del></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/673593893db1d751c26e229dfa74e8f9/29c1d/8.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60.810810810810814%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/673593893db1d751c26e229dfa74e8f9/fcda8/8.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/673593893db1d751c26e229dfa74e8f9/12f09/8.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/673593893db1d751c26e229dfa74e8f9/e4a3f/8.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/673593893db1d751c26e229dfa74e8f9/fcda8/8.png 590w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/673593893db1d751c26e229dfa74e8f9/efc66/8.png 885w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/673593893db1d751c26e229dfa74e8f9/c83ae/8.png 1180w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/673593893db1d751c26e229dfa74e8f9/29c1d/8.png 1375w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h1>什么是 npm</h1>\n<p>npm<del>是\"您配吗\",呸</del> 是 Node Package Manager，也就是 Node 的包管理器。</p>\n<p>了解过<code>python</code>的同学可能知道<code>pip</code>，<code>npm</code>和他有点类似。但是 pip 的包下载后是全局的，npm 可以将依赖（或者称它为包）可以下载到工作区或者下载到全局。</p>\n<p>一般来说，安装了<code>node</code>后，<code>npm</code>也安装好了。可以使用<code>npm -v</code>确认一下。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 278px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/927f9d2068deb5ea7384011e46371eb8/4e29d/9.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 43.24324324324324%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/927f9d2068deb5ea7384011e46371eb8/4e29d/9.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/927f9d2068deb5ea7384011e46371eb8/12f09/9.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/927f9d2068deb5ea7384011e46371eb8/4e29d/9.png 278w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 278px) 100vw, 278px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h1>npm 官网</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/\">https://www.npmjs.com/</a></p>\n<p>npm 是世界上最大的包管理<del>不是我瞎说的，官网写的</del>。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/70c5733996e6687ef84da2ab55a63789/52576/10.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 72.97297297297297%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/70c5733996e6687ef84da2ab55a63789/fcda8/10.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/70c5733996e6687ef84da2ab55a63789/12f09/10.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/70c5733996e6687ef84da2ab55a63789/e4a3f/10.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/70c5733996e6687ef84da2ab55a63789/fcda8/10.png 590w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/70c5733996e6687ef84da2ab55a63789/efc66/10.png 885w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/70c5733996e6687ef84da2ab55a63789/c83ae/10.png 1180w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/70c5733996e6687ef84da2ab55a63789/52576/10.png 1412w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Relied upon by more than 11 million developers worldwide, npm is committed to making JavaScript development elegant, productive, and safe. The free npm Registry has become the center of JavaScript code sharing, and with more than one million packages, the largest software registry in the world. Our other tools and services take the Registry, and the work you do around it, to the next level.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>我们也可以在这上边寻找我们一些其他人的造好的轮子，像一些前端开发框架的脚手架<code>@vue/cli</code>,<code>create-react-app</code>之类的，还有 node.js 后端框架<code>express</code>,<code>koa</code>,<code>egg</code>之类的，以及一些其他好用的工具。</p>\n<h1>一些其他的包管理</h1>\n<p><code>npm</code>也有一些令人诟病的地方，像安装速度慢，依赖关系树，镜像以及其他之类的问题，因此出现了一些其他的 node 的包管理器，像<code>cnpm</code> ,<code>yarn</code> 之类的，可以去了解一下。</p>\n<h1>package.json</h1>\n<p>这是一个 node 项目或者说是一个 npm 包的必备的文件。它包含了项目的必要的信息，以及这个项目所依赖的一些的依赖。</p>\n<p>在终端中进入项目所在的目录，输入<code>npm init -y</code>\n就可以一键生成配置文件。\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/1b23570af4439776041b471a81b92d59/23296/11.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/1b23570af4439776041b471a81b92d59/fcda8/11.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/1b23570af4439776041b471a81b92d59/12f09/11.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/1b23570af4439776041b471a81b92d59/e4a3f/11.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/1b23570af4439776041b471a81b92d59/fcda8/11.png 590w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/1b23570af4439776041b471a81b92d59/23296/11.png 675w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>一些重要的字段像<code>scripts</code>,<code>dependencies</code>,<code>devDependencies</code>有必要了解。</p>\n<p>可以参考这个， <a href=\"https://javascript.ruanyifeng.com/nodejs/packagejson.html\">https://javascript.ruanyifeng.com/nodejs/packagejson.html</a></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>字段名</th>\n<th>作用</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>scripts</td>\n<td>指定了运行脚本命令的 npm 命令行缩写，比如 start 指定了运行<code>npm run start</code>时，所要执行的命令</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>dependencies</td>\n<td>指定了项目运行所依赖的模块</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>devDependencies</td>\n<td>指定项目开发所需要的模块</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h1>如何使用 node.js 过滤问卷名单</h1>\n<p>这就当是一个简单的使用 node.js 的例子吧。我们的寒假项目需要非科协的同学填写问卷，但是有科协的同学填写了问卷，这时我们就需要过滤人员的名单。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/706be325a8ec5d27bc4a76b330b856df/c1c45/12.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 119.59459459459461%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/706be325a8ec5d27bc4a76b330b856df/fcda8/12.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/706be325a8ec5d27bc4a76b330b856df/12f09/12.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/706be325a8ec5d27bc4a76b330b856df/e4a3f/12.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/706be325a8ec5d27bc4a76b330b856df/fcda8/12.png 590w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/706be325a8ec5d27bc4a76b330b856df/c1c45/12.png 824w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>我们简单看一下这个需求，我们需要读取一个 excel，然后过滤\"隔壁软软-钟敏睿\"，重新生成一个新的 excel。</p>\n<p>那么我们怎么使用 node.js 读取 excel 呢。首先作为一个<del>调包侠，呸</del> 优秀的程序员，我们需要去看一下有什么其他大佬写好的代码可以用。我使用的是<a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/node-xlsx\">node-xlsx</a></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/707068d7c5a04fa16d631dd6fb97bdfa/4a70a/13.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.72972972972974%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/707068d7c5a04fa16d631dd6fb97bdfa/fcda8/13.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/707068d7c5a04fa16d631dd6fb97bdfa/12f09/13.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/707068d7c5a04fa16d631dd6fb97bdfa/e4a3f/13.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/707068d7c5a04fa16d631dd6fb97bdfa/fcda8/13.png 590w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/707068d7c5a04fa16d631dd6fb97bdfa/efc66/13.png 885w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/707068d7c5a04fa16d631dd6fb97bdfa/c83ae/13.png 1180w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/707068d7c5a04fa16d631dd6fb97bdfa/4a70a/13.png 2390w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>我们进入项目后，执行<code>npm install --save node-xlsx</code></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/c82ed123cb0b9b78c8c0ffe3b