"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 64.1891891891892%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/e375147d6e20d62856ab4e89913d8922/fcda8/15.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/e375147d6e20d62856ab4e89913d8922/12f09/15.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/e375147d6e20d62856ab4e89913d8922/e4a3f/15.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/e375147d6e20d62856ab4e89913d8922/fcda8/15.png 590w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/e375147d6e20d62856ab4e89913d8922/efc66/15.png 885w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/e375147d6e20d62856ab4e89913d8922/eb2af/15.png 954w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>再根据 node-xlsx 的文档，写出代码。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/cf9a100ea1655a54717f9a650c848148/12e1b/16.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.72972972972974%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/cf9a100ea1655a54717f9a650c848148/fcda8/16.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/cf9a100ea1655a54717f9a650c848148/12f09/16.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/cf9a100ea1655a54717f9a650c848148/e4a3f/16.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/cf9a100ea1655a54717f9a650c848148/fcda8/16.png 590w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/cf9a100ea1655a54717f9a650c848148/efc66/16.png 885w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/cf9a100ea1655a54717f9a650c848148/c83ae/16.png 1180w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/cf9a100ea1655a54717f9a650c848148/12e1b/16.png 1607w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>。</p>\n<p>运行<code>node index.js</code>，就得到了我们要的东西。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/ec1319c53d3e697f19f9cdeff1e1465c/21482/17.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.70270270270271%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/ec1319c53d3e697f19f9cdeff1e1465c/fcda8/17.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/ec1319c53d3e697f19f9cdeff1e1465c/12f09/17.png 148w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/ec1319c53d3e697f19f9cdeff1e1465c/e4a3f/17.png 295w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/ec1319c53d3e697f19f9cdeff1e1465c/fcda8/17.png 590w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/ec1319c53d3e697f19f9cdeff1e1465c/efc66/17.png 885w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/ec1319c53d3e697f19f9cdeff1e1465c/c83ae/17.png 1180w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ChenKS12138/ChenKS12138.github.io/static/ec1319c53d3e697f19f9cdeff1e1465c/21482/17.png 1350w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>。</p>\n<p>到这里，我们就实现了需求，这只是冰山一角，node.js 能做的事情还很多。</p>\n<h1>如何运行别人的 node 项目</h1>\n<p>我们将代码上传至 GitHub 时，一般都会将依赖之类的文件添加进<code>.gitignore</code>。所以每次 clone 一个 node 项目我们都需要重新下载依赖。例如，上面的那个过滤问卷名单的例子 🌰，我已经将代码放到了 GitHub 上。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/ChenKS12138/node-demo-tutorial\">https://github.com/ChenKS12138/node-demo-tutorial</a></p>\n<p>我们 clone 了这个仓库后，文件目录应该如下，没有<code>node_modules</code>。因此我们需要下载依赖。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>.\n├── README.md\n├── data\n│ └── source.xlsx\n├── index.js\n├── package-lock.json\n└── package.json</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>运行<code>npm install</code>就可以下载依赖了。</p>\n<h1>结语</h1>\n<p>node 能做的事情还很多，这个只是一小部分。至此，你已经打开的新世界的大门。</p>","id":"2a5503bf-4c05-5301-82f8-ca1670eb4060","headings":[{"value":"前言","depth":1},{"value":"环境安装","depth":1},{"value":"初次使用","depth":1},{"value":"node 环境和浏览器环境的区别","depth":1},{"value":"什么是 npm","depth":1},{"value":"npm 官网","depth":1},{"value":"一些其他的包管理","depth":1},{"value":"package.json","depth":1},{"value":"如何使用 node.js 过滤问卷名单","depth":1},{"value":"如何运行别人的 node 项目","depth":1},{"value":"结语","depth":1}],"date":"Tuesday, January 14, 2020 9:14 PM","tags":["JavaScript","Node.js"],"title":"Node.js入门指北"}},"staticQueryHashes":["63159454"]}